  "title": "Trailer Truck Driver (Class 4, Construction)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Operate trailer trucks and low-bed vehicles safely on public roads and construction sites.</li><li>Transport and handle materials for both internal and external project requirements.</li><li>Ensure proper upkeep and cleanliness of assigned vehicles, trailers, and equipment.</li><li>Comply with all workplace safety, health, and traffic regulations.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Possess a valid <strong>Class 4 driving licence</strong> with proven trailer driving experience.</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant driving experience in <strong>construction site environments.</strong></li><li>Demonstrate a responsible, safety-conscious attitude and strict adherence to road traffic laws.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
